  fragmentClue: 'Fragment 1 - INSERT INTO


    To add records into a table we use:


    INSERT
    INTO table_name (column1, column2, column3, ...)

    VALUES (value1, value2,
    value3, ...);


    The hacker used table:

    employees


    next fragment:

    ''Where
    workers rest and coffee is poured, the next clue waits near snacks stored''

'
